article.description: — David Duke had 28 points and Nate Watson added 20 points as Providence topped Fairleigh Dickinson 79-67 on Saturday.
article.headline: Duke carries Providence over Fairleigh Dickinson 79-67
article.linkText: Duke carries Providence over Fairleigh Dickinson 79-67
article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- — David Duke had 28 points and Nate Watson added 20 points as Providence topped Fairleigh Dickinson 79-67 on Saturday. Duke hit 10 of 12 free throws for Providence (3-2). Elyjah Williams had 15 points for the Knights (0-4). Jahlil Jenkins added 13 points and Brandon Rush had 12. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
